<article class="elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-2295 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news-zh" role="listitem">
<a class="elementor-post__thumbnail__link" href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e8%90%ac%e8%81%96%e7%8b%82%e6%ad%a1%e5%98%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%8f%af/" tabindex="-1" target=&quot;_blank&quot;>
<div class="elementor-post__thumbnail"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="2560" height="1600" src="https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2365" alt="" srcset="https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party.jpg 2560w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party-300x188.jpg 300w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party-768x480.jpg 768w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party-2048x1280.jpg 2048w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party-1200x750.jpg 1200w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party-1980x1238.jpg 1980w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party-24x15.jpg 24w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party-36x23.jpg 36w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Halloween-costume-party-48x30.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></div>
</a>
<div class="elementor-post__text">
<h3 class="elementor-post__title">
<a href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e8%90%ac%e8%81%96%e7%8b%82%e6%ad%a1%e5%98%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%8f%af/" target=&quot;_blank&quot;>
萬聖狂歡嘉年華			</a>
</h3>
<div class="elementor-post__excerpt">
<p>學生於萬聖狂歡嘉年華當日，穿著不一樣的萬聖節服飾，裝扮成趣怪的樣子，發揮扮演的天份。透過不同的萬聖節遊戲和手工藝活動，讓小朋友充份感受這獨特的節日氣氛。</p>
</div>
<a class="elementor-post__read-more" href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e8%90%ac%e8%81%96%e7%8b%82%e6%ad%a1%e5%98%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%8f%af/" aria-label="Read more about 萬聖狂歡嘉年華" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">
更多 »		</a>
</div>
</article>
<article class="elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-2403 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news-zh" role="listitem">
<a class="elementor-post__thumbnail__link" href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e8%a6%aa%e5%ad%90%e8%8a%b1%e7%87%88%e8%a8%ad%e8%a8%88%e6%af%94%e8%b3%bd/" tabindex="-1" target=&quot;_blank&quot;>
<div class="elementor-post__thumbnail"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1824" height="1157" src="https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Mid-Autumn-Festival-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2457" alt="" srcset="https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Mid-Autumn-Festival-2.jpg 1824w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Mid-Autumn-Festival-2-300x190.jpg 300w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Mid-Autumn-Festival-2-1024x650.jpg 1024w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Mid-Autumn-Festival-2-768x487.jpg 768w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Mid-Autumn-Festival-2-1536x974.jpg 1536w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Mid-Autumn-Festival-2-1200x761.jpg 1200w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Mid-Autumn-Festival-2-24x15.jpg 24w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Mid-Autumn-Festival-2-36x23.jpg 36w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Mid-Autumn-Festival-2-48x30.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 1824px) 100vw, 1824px" /></div>
</a>
<div class="elementor-post__text">
<h3 class="elementor-post__title">
<a href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e8%a6%aa%e5%ad%90%e8%8a%b1%e7%87%88%e8%a8%ad%e8%a8%88%e6%af%94%e8%b3%bd/" target=&quot;_blank&quot;>
親子花燈設計比賽			</a>
</h3>
<div class="elementor-post__excerpt">
<p>親子花燈設計比賽中，家長與學生的參賽作品加入了不同的物料及設計元素，作品極具創意 。</p>
</div>
<a class="elementor-post__read-more" href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e8%a6%aa%e5%ad%90%e8%8a%b1%e7%87%88%e8%a8%ad%e8%a8%88%e6%af%94%e8%b3%bd/" aria-label="Read more about 親子花燈設計比賽" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">
更多 »		</a>
</div>
</article>
<article class="elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-2349 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news-zh" role="listitem">
<a class="elementor-post__thumbnail__link" href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e7%95%a2%e6%a5%ad%e5%85%b8%e7%a6%ae%e6%b4%bb%e5%8b%95/" tabindex="-1" target=&quot;_blank&quot;>
<div class="elementor-post__thumbnail"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="2560" height="1600" src="https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2377" alt="" srcset="https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony.jpg 2560w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony-300x188.jpg 300w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony-768x480.jpg 768w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony-2048x1280.jpg 2048w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony-1200x750.jpg 1200w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony-1980x1238.jpg 1980w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony-24x15.jpg 24w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony-36x23.jpg 36w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Graduation-Ceremony-48x30.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></div>
</a>
<div class="elementor-post__text">
<h3 class="elementor-post__title">
<a href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e7%95%a2%e6%a5%ad%e5%85%b8%e7%a6%ae%e6%b4%bb%e5%8b%95/" target=&quot;_blank&quot;>
畢業典禮活動			</a>
</h3>
<div class="elementor-post__excerpt">
<p>本年畢業典禮充滿了愛和美好的回憶，三年的幼稚園生活中，孩子在歡樂及温馨的校園生活下健康快樂地成長，非常感謝各家長對我們的厚愛及支持。</p>
</div>
<a class="elementor-post__read-more" href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e7%95%a2%e6%a5%ad%e5%85%b8%e7%a6%ae%e6%b4%bb%e5%8b%95/" aria-label="Read more about 畢業典禮活動" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">
更多 »		</a>
</div>
</article>
<article class="elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-2396 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news-zh" role="listitem">
<a class="elementor-post__thumbnail__link" href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e6%a8%a1%e6%93%ac%e5%b9%b4%e5%ae%b5%e6%94%a4%e4%bd%8d%e6%b4%bb%e5%8b%95/" tabindex="-1" target=&quot;_blank&quot;>
<div class="elementor-post__thumbnail"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="640" src="https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Lunar-New-Year-Fair.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2397" alt="" srcset="https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Lunar-New-Year-Fair.jpg 1024w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Lunar-New-Year-Fair-300x188.jpg 300w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Lunar-New-Year-Fair-768x480.jpg 768w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Lunar-New-Year-Fair-24x15.jpg 24w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Lunar-New-Year-Fair-36x23.jpg 36w, https://www.mink.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Lunar-New-Year-Fair-48x30.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></div>
</a>
<div class="elementor-post__text">
<h3 class="elementor-post__title">
<a href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e6%a8%a1%e6%93%ac%e5%b9%b4%e5%ae%b5%e6%94%a4%e4%bd%8d%e6%b4%bb%e5%8b%95/" target=&quot;_blank&quot;>
模擬年宵攤位活動			</a>
</h3>
<div class="elementor-post__excerpt">
<p>模擬年宵攤位活動，學生有很多創作、討論及分享的機會，除了讓學生了解到新年習俗外，亦讓學生學習如何與人溝通的技巧，豐富他們的學習經驗。</p>
</div>
<a class="elementor-post__read-more" href="https://www.mink.edu.hk/%e6%a8%a1%e6%93%ac%e5%b9%b4%e5%ae%b5%e6%94%a4%e4%bd%8d%e6%b4%bb%e5%8b%95/" aria-label="Read more about 模擬年宵攤位活動" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">
更多 »		</a>
</div>
</article>
